cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with human activity recognition from RGB data using a visual attention module. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a method that uses recurrent tracking/recognition workers to jointly perform motion tracking and activity prediction. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a method that uses an external memory module to optimize coherence of the assignments in space, time and feature space. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper deals with recognizing human activities from RGB data. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with tracking and integrating unstructured data, which is relevant to robotics applications.
